<item>
            <title>[DERBY-3554] Change Collation test to run DatabaseMetaDataTest, BatchUpdateTest,GroupByExpressionTest, and UpdateableResultSetTest for only one locale</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3554</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently CollationTest runs DatabaseMetaDataTest, BatchUpdateTest,GroupByExpressionTest, and UpdateableResultSetTest for multiple locales and territory based collation.  It would be sufficient for these to run with a single locale and would save some time running tests.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
